SOURCE: https://github.com/stmicroelectronics/stm32cubeh5/blob/main/Projects/STM32H573I-DK/Applications/USBX/Ux_Device_DFU/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: Other
CODE:
```
._threadx_heap :
  {
     . = ALIGN(8);
     __RAM_segment_used_end__ = .;
     . = . + 64K;
     . = ALIGN(8);
   } >RAM_D1 AT> RAM_D1
```

