TITLE: STM32CubeIDE Linker File Modification
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to add a new section named ._threadx_heap to the STM32CubeIDE linker file (.ld) for ThreadX dynamic memory allocation.  It allocates 64KB of RAM to the heap and aligns it to 8 bytes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/stmicroelectronics/stm32cubeh5/blob/main/Projects/NUCLEO-H533RE/Applications/ThreadX/Tx_Thread_Creation/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: linker
CODE:
```
._threadx_heap :
  {
     . = ALIGN(8);
     __RAM_segment_used_end__ = .;
     . = . + 64K;
     . = ALIGN(8);
   } >RAM_D1 AT> RAM_D1
```

