TITLE: ThreadX Memory Allocation Configuration - STM32CubeIDE
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to add a new section in the STM32CubeIDE linker file to allocate memory for the ThreadX heap. It defines a `._threadx_heap` section, sets its size to 64KB, and locates it between the `.bss` and `._user_heap_stack` sections in the `RAM_D1` memory region.
