LANGUAGE: Assembly
CODE:
```
    PUBLIC  your_assembly_isr
your_assembly_isr:

    PUSH    {r0, lr}

    ; ISR processing goes here, including any needed function calls.

    POP     {r0, lr}
    BX      lr
```

