TITLE: STM32CubeIDE Linker Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to add a new section named '._threadx_heap' to the STM32CubeIDE linker file (.ld). This section is used to define a memory region for ThreadX's heap. It sets the alignment, defines the end of the RAM segment used, allocates 64KB of memory for the heap, and specifies that this region is located in and loaded from 'RAM_D1'.
