TITLE: Configuring RFFT Options (Q31) in CMake
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines CMake options to enable or disable Real FFT (RFFT) implementations for Q31 data types with various sizes (32 to 8192). These options are used to customize the CMSIS-DSP library by selecting specific RFFT implementations for different sizes.
