TITLE: Linker Configuration for STM32CubeIDE
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the necessary linker configuration for STM32CubeIDE to provide memory for ThreadX. It defines a new section named ._threadx_heap within the RAM_D1 memory region, allocating 64KB for the ThreadX heap. The ._threadx_heap must be located between the .bss and the ._user_heap_stack sections in the linker script.
