TITLE: STM32CubeIDE linker file modification for ThreadX
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the modification needed in the STM32CubeIDE linker (.ld) file to enable dynamic memory allocation for ThreadX. It adds a new section named `._threadx_heap` in the RAM_D1 region and sets its size to 64KB. The section must be placed between the .bss and ._user_heap_stack sections to ensure proper memory allocation for ThreadX.
SOURCE: https://github.com/stmicroelectronics/stm32cubeh5/blob/main/Projects/STM32H573I-DK/Applications/FileX/Fx_MultiAccess/README.md#_snippet_2

