TITLE: STM32CubeIDE Linker Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This configuration defines a new section named ._threadx_heap in the STM32CubeIDE linker file to provide memory for ThreadX. The memory is allocated in the RAM_D1 region and its size is set to 64KB.
SOURCE: https://github.com/stmicroelectronics/stm32cubeh5/blob/main/Projects/STM32H573I-DK/Applications/ThreadX/Tx_Thread_Creation/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: LD
CODE:
```
._threadx_heap :
  {
    . = ALIGN(8);
    __RAM_segment_used_end__ = .;
    . = . + 64K;
    . = ALIGN(8);
  } >RAM_D1 AT> RAM_D1
```

