TITLE: Header File Symbolic Linking
DESCRIPTION: This snippet creates symbolic links to the header files in the ThreadX include directories to a common include directory within the build directory. This simplifies including header files in other parts of the project.
SOURCE: https://github.com/stmicroelectronics/stm32cubeh5/blob/main/Middlewares/ST/netxduo/test/cmake/nx_secure/libs/CMakeLists.txt#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: cmake
CODE:
```
get_target_property(dirs threadx INCLUDE_DIRECTORIES)
execute_process(COMMAND mkdir -p ${CMAKE_BINARY_DIR}/inc)
foreach(dir ${dirs})
  file(GLOB header_files ${dir}/*.h)
  foreach(header_file ${header_files})
    execute_process(COMMAND ln -sf ${header_file} ${CMAKE_BINARY_DIR}/inc)
  endforeach()
endforeach()
```

