TITLE: Create Symbolic Links for Header Files
DESCRIPTION: This snippet iterates through the ThreadX and FileX libraries, retrieves their include directories, and creates symbolic links to all header files in those directories within a common 'inc' directory in the build directory. This allows easy access to all library headers during compilation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/stmicroelectronics/stm32cubeh5/blob/main/Middlewares/ST/netxduo/test/cmake/libs/CMakeLists.txt#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: CMake
CODE:
```
foreach(lib threadx filex)
  get_target_property(dirs ${lib} INCLUDE_DIRECTORIES)
  execute_process(COMMAND mkdir -p ${CMAKE_BINARY_DIR}/inc)
  foreach(dir ${dirs})
    file(GLOB header_files ${dir}/*.h)
    foreach(header_file ${header_files})
      execute_process(COMMAND ln -sf ${header_file} ${CMAKE_BINARY_DIR}/inc)
    endforeach()
  endforeach()
endforeach()
```

