TITLE: Remove Addons from Sources
DESCRIPTION: This snippet removes source files containing 'addons' in their path from the `netxduo` target. This is done by iterating through the existing source list, filtering out any files matching the pattern, and then updating the target's source property with the filtered list.
SOURCE: https://github.com/stmicroelectronics/stm32cubeh5/blob/main/Middlewares/ST/netxduo/test/cmake/nx_secure/CMakeLists.txt#_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: CMake
CODE:
```
get_target_property(SOURCES_LIST netxduo SOURCES)
set(NEW_SOURCES_LIST "")
foreach(SOURCE ${SOURCES_LIST})
  if(NOT ("${SOURCE}" MATCHES ".*addons.*"))
    list(APPEND NEW_SOURCES_LIST ${SOURCE})
  endif()
endforeach()
set_target_properties(netxduo PROPERTIES SOURCES "${NEW_SOURCES_LIST}")
```

