TITLE: Managing NetX Duo Sources
DESCRIPTION: This snippet retrieves the list of source files and the source directory from the `netxduo` target. It then iterates through a list of directories to exclude, removing their source files from the build to create a more focused build tailored for testing. It utilizes `aux_source_directory` to identify source files in excluded directories, and `list(REMOVE_ITEM)` to remove those files from the overall source list.
